This Frederic Lansac French XXX film is one of Brigitte Lahaie's very best. Not only is Brigitte is top form (as ever), but she is surrounded
by several other lovely young lasses in schoolgirl uniforms (including the beautiful Marlyn Jess, who performs a brilliant bound-and-gagged
